UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2275
1 member appointed by the Minority Floor Leader of the Senate;
2 (3) The Attorney General;
3 (4) The secretary of the Public Protection Cabinet;
4 (5) One member representing the Kentucky County Clerks Association;
5 (6) One member representing the Kentucky Association of Realtors;
6 (7) One member representing mortgage brokers; and
7 (8) One member representing title companies.
8 Section 3. The Real Estate Modernization Task Force shall meet at least
9 monthly during the 2026 Interim of the General Assembly and shall submit its findings,
10 legislative recommendations, or a memorandum to the Legislative Research Commission
11 no later than December 1, 2026. If legislative recommendations are submitted, the
12 Legislative Research Commission may refer the recommendations to the appropriate
13 committee or committees of jurisdiction in advance of the 2027 Regular Session of the
14 General Assembly.
